Emporer Ssra.<br>
<br>
Now that Planes of Power is out Wizard's are finding ourselves out of <br>
balance slightly to other classes.<br>
<br>
To correct this the best solution would be to change these 2 spells to <br>
drop off the normal SoL Loot Table.<br>
<br>
Please respond Thanks appreicate your time and effort in this matter<br>
